reviews.review_text: Great audience recording! MOTB strikes again...great 1985 audience recording...loud, clear, and awesome 3-d stereo!
Great Recording, Great Show, Great Venue I was at this show.  I've gotten several copies of it since.  This one is the best.  Thanks for the excellent recording and great memories.
Thanks for posting Mark It's nice to have digital recordings of all the taspes I had copied from you over the years.  Thanks Dude....
Phase Terrific show -- but for some reason the channels are out of phase.  If you download the files and flip the signal on one of the channels the show will sound a lot better.
